<p>2.<a href="https://github.com/QSCTech" rel="external nofollow" target="_blank">浙大项目传送门</a><br>3.<a href="https://github.com/PKUanonym" rel="external nofollow" target="_blank">清华大学共享了计算机系课程资源</a><br>4.<a href="https://github.com/mbinary" rel="external nofollow" target="_blank">中科大共享了计算机学院的课程资源</a></p>
